    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "this is not an accepted method of expanding a DataFrame, *only* loc is available on a ``DataFrame``, see the docs: http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/indexing.html#setting-with-enlargement\r\n\r\nThe reason is you are actually doing 2 operations when you do:\r\n\r\n``df.x[1]``, similar to how setting with copy is an undetectable condition. I don't know that you can actually detect that this is an expansion w/o a lot of gymnastics. So why this is observed undesirable behavior, it is not supported."
  },
